data.description: NEW PRICE AND SELLER IS OFFERING UP TO $7500 TOWARDS 2-1 INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER!  Welcome to the epitome of luxury living in the sought-after Trailmark community! This exquisite Providence-built 2-story residence boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and an expansive 2,400 sq. ft. of meticulously crafted living space.  Step into culinary perfection with the gourmet kitchen, adorned with quartz countertops, a marble backsplash, under cabinet lighting, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, including a convenient wall oven and microwave. The downstairs living space features elegant ceramic tile flooring and introduces a versatile non-conforming 4th bedroom with French doors, perfect for a den or home office. Ascend the grand staircase, where rich wood flooring leads you to a spacious loft area that doubles as a second living room, creating an ideal retreat for relaxation. The sleeping quarters offer tranquility and comfort, highlighted by a large primary bedroom boasting a trey ceiling and an equally expansive primary bath.  Escape to the outdoors through the screened-in lanai, unveiling a well-maintained, fully fenced backyard. Here, one can unwind around the firepit, creating memorable moments in a private and serene setting.  Additional features include gutters, a tankless water heater, a water softener and a convenient 2-car garage, providing both functionality and style. Immerse yourself in the Trailmark community, which offers a resort-style pool, clubhouse, exercise room, scenic walking paths, a kayak launch, dog park, basketball courts, and volleyball courts. Trailmark is also a natural gas community.  Don't miss the chance to make this extraordinary residence your forever home. Schedule a visit, fall in love with the unmatched elegance, and make an offer – your Trailmark dream home awaits!
